com.collabnet.ccf.core
Class EntityService

java.lang.Object
  com.collabnet.ccf.core.EntityService
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.openadaptor.core.IDataProcessor
public class EntityService
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.openadaptor.core.IDataProcessor

This component will find out whether an artifact coming out of the source system has to be created, updated, deleted or ignored within the target system. It will also try to find out the correct id of the artifact on the target system.

jnicolai
